OL,6,FA couple who opened up their private
OL,7,Fswimming pool for public use are
OL,8,Ffacing a battle to keep welcoming
OL,9,Fcustomers after they were told they
OL,10,Fare breaching planning rules.
OL,12,FJon and Paula Gardiner started
OL,13,Foffering paid-for sessions at their
OL,14,Fhome in Ossett, West Yorkshire, to
OL,15,Fcover mounting running costs.
