OL,3,CCouple who opened private pool to the
OL,4,Cpublic face planning fight
OL,6,FThey said demand from interested
OL,7,Fswimmers quickly became "phenomenal" `
OL,8,Ffollowing the closure of other
OL,9,Fpublicly run facilities in the area `
OL,10,Fwith 250 enquiries within 24 hours of
OL,11,Fadvertising on social media.
OL,13,FBut the couple are having to campaign
OL,14,Fto keep the pool open after being told
OL,15,Fthey need commercial planning approval.
OL,17,FTheir planning application has
OL,18,Fattracted more than 160 comments of
OL,19,Fsupport on the Wakefield Council
OL,20,Fwebsite, but more than 50 objections.
