OL,3,CCouple who opened private pool to the
OL,4,Cpublic face planning fight
OL,6,FMr Gardiner said there was huge demand
OL,7,Ffor their facility.
OL,9,F"Local pools such as Ossett Academy,
OL,10,Fwhere swimming lessons were held up to
OL,11,Ftwo years ago, that has since shut,
OL,12,Fand they closed Dewsbury swimming
OL,13,Fbaths, which is about three and a half
OL,14,Fmiles from here," he said.
OL,16,F"So the demand was phenomenal, I
OL,17,Fcouldn't believe how many people
OL,18,Fwanted to hire the pool in my back
OL,19,Fgarden."
