OL,4,Cpublic face planning fight
OL,6,FThey need additional permission
OL,7,Fbecause charging customers to use it
OL,8,Fis classed as a change of use.
OL,10,FThey were told to submit a new
OL,11,Fapplication after advertising their
OL,12,Fventure in October.
OL,14,FWakefield District Housing, which
OL,15,Fmanages social housing in the area, is
OL,16,Famong the objectors.
OL,18,FIn its official comment, it said the
OL,19,Fpool could "potentially restrict
OL,20,Faccess and cause disturbance" to
OL,21,Felderly residents.
