OL,3,CCouple who opened private pool to the
OL,4,Cpublic face planning fight
OL,6,F"We also have issues with parking in
OL,7,Fthe area, blocking access which could
OL,8,Fresult in assisting a potentially
OL,9,Funwell and vulnerable person should an
OL,10,Femergency vehicle not be able to
OL,11,Faccess the property.".JLocal resident
OL,12,FPam Grace said: "One of our main
OL,13,Fconcerns is that at Station Road,
OL,14,Fwhich is the other side of the
OL,15,Fbuilding, there's a gate to our
OL,16,Fproperty, and people have been parking
OL,17,Fthere and coming through our garden to
OL,18,Fget through to there."
