OL,6,FAnother resident, Margaret Blockley,
OL,7,Fadded: "The shortcuts, which they have
OL,8,Fto pass my living room window, my
OL,9,Fbedroom window, my kitchen window at
OL,10,Fclose quarters, and I feel
OL,11,Fthreatened."JHowever, dozens of users
OL,12,Fhave spoken out in support of the
OL,13,FGardiners.
OL,15,FElizabeth Morris said: "I've got a
OL,16,Fslight disability and the pool and the
OL,17,Fwarmth, it's perfect for me."JVal
OL,18,FNewman added: "We were always told the
OL,19,FOssett would get a leisure centre, and
OL,20,Fit's never materialised. So there
OL,21,Fisn't anything local that's like this."
